hat%20the%20education%20body%20is%20considering%20faster%20degree%20completion%20options%20for%20students.%20Speaking%20at%20southern%20zone%20conference%20for%20autonomous%20colleges%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20students%20will%20soon%20be%20allowed%20to%20complete%20a%20three-year-degree%20course%20in%20two-an-a-half%20years%2C%20and%20four-year%20courses%20in%20three.%20The%20one-day%20conference%20was%20organised%20at%20IIT%20Madras%20to%20prepare%20a%20roadmap%20to%20implement%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%20Academicians%20from%20several%20institutions%20took%20part%20on%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20planning%20to%20implement%20this%20from%20the%20next%20academic%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%20when%20asked%20about%20UGC's%20faster%20degree%20completion%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20students%20who%20are%20capable%20can%20complete%20the%20degree%20programmes%20in%20a%20shorter%20duration.%20We%20anticipate%20that%20they%20can%20gain%20six%20months%20to%20one%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%2C%20however%2C%20clarified%20that%20students%20who%20wish%20to%20take%20longer%20to%20complete%20their%20studies%20will%20also%20be%20accommodated%2C%20and%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20breaks%20during%20their%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20is%20based%20on%20the%20recommendation%20made%20by%20IIT%20Madras%20Director%20V%20Kamakoti.%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20detailed%20guidelines%20will%20be%20issued%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20NEP%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20transformation%20of%20education%20system%20that%20will%20benefit%20students%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20onus%20lies%20on%20higher%20education%20institutes%20(HEIs)%20to%20make%20education%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccess%2C%20equity%20and%20inclusivity%20in%20higher%20education%20are%20essential%20determinants%20of%20how%20far%20our%20students%20will%20advance%2C%20take%20up%20positions%20in%20society%20and%20excel%20in%20their%20respective%20professions.%20Educational%20institutions%20must%20ensure%20that%20higher%20education%20is%20affordable%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20supportive%20for%20our%20students%20to%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENEP%20was%20launched%20on%20July%2029%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731656280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F52dgrs2_ugc-chairman-m-jagadesh-kumar_625x300_15_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Funiversity-body-may-allow-4-year-degree-courses-to-be-completed-in-3-years-7024707%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Kumar%2C%20however%2C%20clarified%20that%20students%20who%20wish%20to%20take%20longer%20to%20complete%20their%20studies%20will%20also%20be%20accommodated%2C%20and%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20breaks%20during%20their%20courses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Funiversity-body-may-allow-4-year-degree-courses-to-be-completed-in-3-years-7024707%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWill%20Take%20It%20To%20My%20Grave%26quot%3B%3A%20Narayana%20Murthy%20Firm%20On%20%26quot%3B70-Hour%20Workweek%26quot%3B%20Comment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInfosys%20co-founder%20Narayana%20Murthy%20has%20defended%20his%20controversial%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarayana-murthy-suggests-70-hour-work-week-to-youngsters-sparks-debate-4516739%5C%22%3E70-hour%20workweek%20comments%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20added%20that%20hard%20work%20is%20crucial%20to%20India's%20progress.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20sorry%2C%20I%20have%20not%20changed%20my%20view.%20I%20will%20take%20this%20with%20me%20to%20my%20grave%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Murthy%20said%20at%20the%20C