C%20no%20major%20concern%20with%20Rahul%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731654328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115327018%2Cimgsize-38456.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-australia%2Fvirat-kohli-absolutely-fine-no-major-concern-with-kl-rahul%2Farticleshow%2F115326579.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20Test%20squad%20held%20match%20simulations%20in%20Perth%2C%20with%20Virat%20Kohli%20batting%20without%20any%20discomfort%20following%20a%20precautionary%20scan.%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20however%2C%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20ball%20and%20unable%20to%20continue%20batting%2C%20raising%20minor%20concerns%20ahead%20of%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SAHIL%20MALHOTRA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMy%20Mistake%20To%20Put%20Up%20Wife%20Against%20Supriya%20Sule%26quot%3B%3A%20Ajit%20Pawar%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fajit-pawar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAjit%20Pawar%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadmitted%20that%20it%20was%20a%20mistake%20to%20field%20his%20wife%20Sunetra%20Pawar%20against%20his%20cousin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupriya-sule%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupriya%20Sule%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Ms%20Sule%2C%20daughter%20of%20NCP%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20had%20defeated%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20representing%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20NCP%20faction%2C%20in%20the%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20over%201.5%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20my%20mistake%20to%20field%20her%20against%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20I%20have%20told%20you%20again%20and%20again.%20It%20is%20over%20now.%20On%20November%2020%20there%20is%20an%20election%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20the%20voters%20will%20decide%20in%20whose%20hands%20Maharashtra%20should%20be%20given%20for%20five%20years.%20We%20are%20paying%20more%20attention%20to%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20said%20that%20his%20primary%20focus%20remains%20on%20campaigning%20in%20the%20constituencies%20allotted%20to%20the%20NCP%20under%20the%20Mahayuti%20(Grand%20Alliance).%20The%2065-year-old%20said%20that%20despite%20occasional%20calls%20from%20alliance%20partners%20like%20the%20BJP%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%20to%20join%20their%20campaigns%2C%20he%20is%20prioritising%20NCP%20seats.%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20with%20only%20a%20few%20days%20left%2C%20I%20am%20concentrating%20on%20our%20constituencies%20and%20holding%20public%20rallies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENepotism%20In%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20said%20that%20political%20families%20have%20played%20a%20role%20in%20all%20major%20parties%2C%20from%20Congress%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20(MNS).%20He%20argued%20that%20ultimately%2C%20it%20is%20the%20voters%20who%20decide%20whether%20a%20candidate%20from%20a%20political%20family%20deserves%20their%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-elections-uddhav-thackeray-abandoned-bal-thackerays-ideology-eknath-shinde-to-ndtv-7023544%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories_lastestImg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOn%20Abuse%20Of%20Power%20Charge%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20%26quot%3BHave%20We%20Arrested%20Anyone%26quot%3B%20Counter%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20speaks%20against%20nepotism%2C%20but%20in%20this%20election%2C%20both%20the%20Mahavikas%20Aghadi%20and%20the%20Mahayuti%20alliances%20have%20numerous%20candidates%20from%20political%20families.%20This%20trend%20has%20been%20part%20of%20Indian%20politics%20for%20decades.%20After%20we%20gained%20independence%20in%201947%2C%20the%20families%20who%20initially%20entered%20politics%20continued%20to%20hold%20influence.%20The%20Congress%20party%20dominated%20government%20for%20many%20years%2C%20bringing%20successive%20generations%20into%20its%20ranks%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20across%20all%20parties%20-%20whether%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20BJP%2C%20or%20even%20the%20MNS%20-%20family%20members%20of%20political%20leaders%20are%20running%20for%20office.%20%C2%A0However%2C%20it's%20ultimately%20the%20voters%20who%20decide.%20Regardless%20of%20family%20ties%2C%20voters%20support%20candidates%20they%20believe%20will%20work%20for%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectoral%20Confidence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20also%20expressed%20strong%20confidence%20in%20his%20own%20candidacy%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3B100%20per%20cent%26quot%3B%20secure%20his%20seat%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections.%20Referring%20to%20the%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20where%20a%20%26quot%3Bsympathy%20factor%26quot%3B%20for%20Sharad%20Pawar%20influenced%20outcomes%20in%20Baramati%2C%20he%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20time%2C%20I%20am%20fully%20confident%20of%20winning%20my%20seat.%20I%20am%20certain%20of%20a%20100%20per%20cent%20victory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20elections%20will%20decide%20the%20fate%20of%20288%20seats%2C%20with%20the%20Mahayuti%20coalition%2C%20comprising%20the%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20and%20NCP%2C%20facing%20off%20against%20the%20Mahavikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20alliance%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20and%20NCP%20factions.%20The%202019%20assembly%20polls%20saw%20the%20BJP%20eme