20channels%20into%20Canada%2C%20aimed%20at%20arming%20Khalistani%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20June%202023%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20triggered%20a%20diplomatic%20rift%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20which%20continues%20to%20this%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731648780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fgrqo4c0o_canada-firing-_625x300_15_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F100-rounds-fired-outside-music-studio-in-canadas-toronto-23-arrested-7023939%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20100%20rounds%20were%20fired%20outside%20a%20music%20recording%20studio%20in%20Canada's%20Toronto.%20The%20late-night%20gunfire%20on%20Monday%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%2023%20people%20and%20the%20seizure%20of%2016%20firearms%2C%20including%20two%20assault-style%20rifles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F100-rounds-fired-outside-music-studio-in-canadas-toronto-23-arrested-7023939%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Landslide%20Victory%20For%20Lanka%20President's%20Party%20In%20Snap%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESri%20Lankan%20President%20Anura%20Kumara%20Dissanayake's%20leftist%20coalition%20won%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%20snap%20legislative%20elections%2C%20results%20showed%20Friday%2C%20as%20voters%20repudiated%20establishment%20parties%20blamed%20for%20triggering%20an%20economic%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDissanayake%2C%20a%20self-avowed%20Marxist%2C%20swept%20September%20presidential%20elections%20on%20a%20promise%20to%20combat%20graft%20and%20recover%20stolen%20assets%2C%20two%20years%20after%20a%20slow-motion%20financial%20crash%20imposed%20widespread%20hardships%20on%20the%20island%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20decision%20to%20immediately%20call%20polls%20and%20secure%20parliamentary%20backing%20for%20his%20agenda%20was%20vindicated%20on%20Friday%2C%20with%20his%20National%20People's%20Power%20(NPP)%20coalition%20taking%20at%20least%20123%20seats%20in%20the%20225-member%20assembly%20and%20on%20track%20to%20win%20many%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coalition%20had%20a%20monumental%2062%20percent%20of%20the%20vote%20among%20the%20more%20than%20three-quarters%20of%20ballots%20counted%20so%20far%2C%20while%20opposition%20leader%20Sajith%20Premadasa's%20party%20was%20well%20behind%20with%20only%2018%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20voted%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20corruption%20and%20a%20corrupt%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20IT%20professional%20Chanaka%20Rajapaksha%2C%20who%20supported%20the%20NPP%20in%20the%20polls%2C%20told%20AFP%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20magnitude%20of%20support%20for%20Dissanayake%2C%20his%20party%20won%20the%20most%20votes%20in%20the%20northern%20district%20of%20Jaffna%2C%20dominated%20by%20the%20island's%20minority%20Tamil%20community%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20independence%20from%20Britain%20in%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDissanayake%2C%20the%2055-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20labourer%2C%20said%20he%20expected%20%26quot%3Ba%20strong%20majority%26quot%3B%20in%20parliament%20to%20press%20ahead%20with%20his%20platform%20after%20casting%20his%20ballot%20in%20Thursday's%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20this%20is%20a%20crucial%20election%20that%20will%20mark%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20this%20election%2C%20the%20NPP%20expects%20a%20mandate%20for%20a%20very%20strong%20majority%20in%20parliament.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20nine-hour%20voting%20period%20passed%20without%20any%20incidents%20of%20violence%2C%20unlike%20most%20ballots%20of%20recent%20years%2C%20but%20three%20election%20workers%20including%20a%20police%20constable%20died%20due%20to%20illness%20while%20on%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoter%20turnout%20was%20estimated%20at%20under%2070%20percent%2C%20less%20than%20in%20September%20presidential%20polls%20that%20saw%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20Sri%20Lanka's%20eligible%20voters%20cast%20a%20ballot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDissanayake%20had%20been%20an%20MP%20for%20nearly%2025%20years%20and%20was%20briefly%20an%20agriculture%20minister%20but%20his%20NPP%20coalition%20held%20just%20three%20seats%20in%20the%20outgoing%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stormed%20to%20the%20presidency%20after%20successfully%20distancing%20himself%20from%20establishment%20politicians%20blamed%20for%20steering%20the%20country%20to%20its%202022%20economic%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20financial%20crash%20was%20the%20worst%20in%20Buddhist-majority%20Sri%20Lanka's%20history%20as%20an%20independent%20nation%2C%20sparking%20months-long%20shortages%20of%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20essential%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resulting%20public%20anger%20culminated%20in%20the%20storming%20of%20then-president%20Gotabaya%20Rajapaksa's%20compound%2C%20prompting%20his%20resignation%20and%20temporary%20exile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDissanayake's%20pledge%20to%20change%20a%20%26quot%3Bcorrupt%26quot%3B%20political%20culture%20has%20resonated%20with%20millions%20of%20Sri%20Lankans%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20following%20tax%20hikes%20and%20other%20austerity%20measures%20imposed%20to%20repair%20the%20nation's%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20JVP%20party%2C%20the%20main%20constituent%20in%20the%20NPP%20coalition%2C%20led%20two%20insurrections%20in%201971%20and%201987%20that%20resulted%20in%20at%20least%2080%2C000%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20sworn%20in%20after%20September's%20presidential%20polls%2C%20described%20as%20one%20of%20the%20island%20nation's%20most%20peaceful%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Investor%20confidence'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPortraits%20of%20communist%20luminaries%20including%20Karl%20Marx%2C%20Vladimir%20Lenin%2C%20Friedrich%20Engels%20and%20Fidel%20Castro%20hang%20in%20Dissanayake's%20office%20in%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20rise%20to%20popularity%2C%20however%2C%20he%20has%20softened%20some%20policies%2C%20saying%20he%20believes%20in%20an%20open%20economy%20and%20is%20not%20totally%20opposed%20to%20privatisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDissanayake%20had%20campaigned%20on%20a%20pledge%20to%20renegotiate%20a%20controversial%20%242.9%20billion%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20bailout%20secured%20by%20his%20predecessor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20taking%20office%2C%20he%20has%20resolved%20to%20maintain%20the%20existing%20agreement%20with%20the%20international%20lender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20main%20private%20sector%20lobby%2C%20the%20Ceylon%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%2C%20is%20tacitly%20supporting%20Dissanayake%20and%20his%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESri%20Lanka's%20stock%20exchange%20has%20gained%20over%2016%20percent%20in%20the%20eight%20weeks%20since%20Dissanayake%20won%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Opposition%20is%20dead'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoll%20monitors%20and%20analysts%20said%20Thursday's%20election%20had%20failed%20to%20generate%20the%20level%20of%20enthusiasm%20--%20or%20violence%20--%20seen%20at%20previous%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20opposition%20is%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20political%20analyst%20Kusal%20Perera%20said%20before%20the%20vote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20result%20of%20the%20election%20is%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outgoing%20parliament%20was%20dominated%20by%20Mahinda%20and%20Gotabaya%20Rajapaksa%2C%20two%20brothers%20from%20a%20powerful%20political%20clan%20who%20have%20both%20served%20as%20president%2C%20but%20it%20has%20since%20splintered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Rajapaksa%20is%20contesting%2C%20but%20Mahinda's%20son%20Namal%2C%20a%20former%20sports%20minister%2C%20is%20seeking%20re-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20