times%20that%20of%20the%20median%20annual%20household%20income%20of%20%2497%2C124%2C%20per%20the%20Home%20Attainability%20Index%20report.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FMSPUS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedian%20price%20of%20US%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Q3%202024%20is%20about%205.4%20times%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.census.gov%2Ftable%2FACSST1Y2023.S1901%3Fq%3Dmedian%2520income%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20median%20household%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%2477%2C719%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20chanced%20upon%20the%20listing%20while%20browsing%20for%20homes%20online%2C%20Ng%2C%2044%2C%20told%20BI.%20The%20large%2C%20rectangular%20floor%20plan%20drew%20them%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20had%20been%20divided%20into%20seven%20different%20rooms%20and%20was%20being%20rented%20out%20to%20foreign%20workers%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20rundown%20%E2%80%94%20it%20looked%20nothing%20like%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collage%20of%20an%20old%20bathroom%20and%20a%20dirty%20bedroom%20in%20the%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6736c2eeede4eeae3927bfa9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20house%20had%20previously%20been%20divided%20into%20seven%20rooms.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Amanda%20Misso.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20still%20tenanted%20when%20the%20couple%20showed%20up%20to%20tour%20the%20unit%2C%20Ng%2C%20who%20works%20in%20hospitality%20and%20entertainment%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20came%20in%2C%20the%20agent%20was%20trying%20to%20show%20us%20the%20bedrooms.%20He%20wanted%20to%20knock%20on%20every%20bedroom%20door%20to%20open%20it%2C%20and%20we%20w