atter%20what%20your%20political%20leanings%20are%20and%20how%20much%20of%20your%20knowledge%20of%20history%20is%20coloured%20by%20WhatsApp%20forwards%2C%20you%20will%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20fault%20the%20points%20of%20emphasis%20and%20the%20lines%20of%20argument%20that%20Advani's%20interpretation%20of%20events%20employs%20because%20it%20is%20clearly%20based%20on%20extensive%20research%20and%20a%20book%20that%20got%20everything%20right%2C%20give%20or%20take%20a%20few%20stray%20departures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20anything%20that%20is%20amiss%20in%20%3Cem%3EFreedom%20at%20Midnigh%3C%2Fem%3Et%2C%20it%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20each%20of%20the%20key%20dramatic%20personae%20is%20put%20into%20an%20airtight%20ideological%20block%20that%20represents%20a%20specific%20line%20of%20thinking%20that%20is%20played%20off%20against%20the%20swirling%20forces%20of%20history%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20generating%20drama%20and%20conflict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20is%20the%20sage%2C%20Nehru%20an%20idealist%20committed%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20unified%20India%2C%20Patel%20a%20pragmatist%20who%20believes%20it%20is%20fine%20to%20amputate%20a%20hand%20to%20save%20the%20arm%2C%20and%20Jinnah%20an%20unbudging%20votary%20of%20a%20separate%20nation%20for%20Muslims.%20The%20show%20does%20not%20have%20much%20scope%20for%20these%20remarkable%20men%20to%20succumb%20to%20human%20inconsistencies.%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EFreedom%20at%20Midnight%3C%2Fem%3E%20isn't%20driven%20by%20A-list%20stars%20but%20by%20actors%20who%20painstakingly%20and%20confidently%20flesh%20out%20the%20aforementioned%20towering%20historical%20figures.%20Their%20task%20is%20onerous%2C%20and%20even%20though%20not%20all%20of%20them%20may%20bear%20exact%20resemblance%20to%20the%20leaders%20they%20play%2C%20they%20succeed%20in%20making%20us%20believe%20that%20they%20are%20indeed%20the%20men%20that%20they%20portray.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnSidhant%20Gupta%2C%20who%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20role%20of%20a%20budding%20filmmaker%20in%20Vikramaditya%20Motwane's%20Jubilee%2C%20adds%20another%20feather%20to%20his%20cap%20with%20his%20performance%20as%20Pandit%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20presents%20India's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20as%20a%20suave%20barrister%20who%20is%20perfectly%20at%20home%20in%20the%20rough%20and%20tumble%20of%20politics%20even%20as%20he%20struggles%20to%20wrap%20his%20head%20around%20the%20idea%20of%20cleaving%20the%20subcontinent%20into%20two.%20The%20fact%20that%20Gupta%2C%20a%20thirty-something%20actor%2C%20is%20consistently%20convincing%20as%20Nehru%20in%20his%20late%2050s%2C%20is%20no%20less%20than%20a%20marvel.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnRajendra%20Chawla%20delivers%20on%20all%20fronts%20as%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%2C%20projected%20as%20a%20hardnosed%20man%20of%20action%20who%20readily%20embraces%20the%20proposal%20of%20Partition%20because%20he%20wants%20to%20stop%20the%20seeds%20of%20religious%20hatred%20and%20distrust%20from%20spreading%20across%20the%20country.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnChirag%20Vohra%20is%20a%20bold%20choice%20for%20the%20character%20of%20Mohandas%20Karamchand%20Gandhi.%20It%20comes%20off%20because%20once%20the%20wall%20of%20disbelief%20is%20breached%2C%20he%20grows%20on%20the%20audience.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnAt%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%20is%20Arif%20Zakaria%20as%20a%20tubercular%20Mohammed%20Ali%20Jinnah.%20Although%20the%20character%20is%20bereft%20of%20shades%2C%20the%20actor%20is%20never%20short%20of%20impressive.%20He%20is%20the%20least%20conflicted%20of%20the%20main%20players%20in%20Freedom%20at%20Midnight%20and%20yet%20Zakaria%20manages%20to%20impart%20to%20him%20significant%20angularities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Jinnah's%20younger%20sister%20Fatima%20(Ira%20Dubey%2C%20one%20of%20the%20few%20women%20in%20the%20cast%20who%20isn't%20relegated%20to%20the%20sidelines)%20points%20out%20to%20him%20that%20regional%20identity%20is%20stronger%20than%20the%20religious%20one%2C%20he%20brushes%20it%20off%20without%20letting%20the%20argument%20go%20any%20further.%20He%20goes%20in%20just%20one%20direction%20and%20nowhere%20else%20and%20that%20robs%20the%20portrayal%20of%20nuance.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20that%20certainly%20isn't%20the%20bane%20of%20the%20series%20as%20a%20whole.%20%3Cem%3EFreedom%20at%20Midnight%3C%2Fem%3E%20chooses%20sustained%20engagement%20over%20mere%20entertainment%20as%20it%20makes%20its%20way%20through%20the%20battlefield%20on%20which%20the%20clash%20between%20conflicting%20notions%20of%20nation%20and%20identity%20played%20out%20and%20presents%20a%20composite%20of%20resonant%2C%20eternally%20relevant%20notions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20historical%20drama%20can%20be%20deemed%20successful%20unless%20it%20contains%20within%20its%20folds%20the%20lessons%20that%20are%20to%20be%20learnt%20from%20the%20watersheds%20that%20shape%20nations%2C%20communities%20and%20political%20formations.%20%3Cem%3EFreedom%20at%20Midnight%3C%2Fem%3E%20does%20not%20fail%20to%20dwell%20upon%20the%20consequences%20of%20decisions%20taken%20under%20duress%20and%20in%20response%20to%20raging%20conflagrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20series%20depicts%20events%20that%20occurred%20over%2075%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20has%20many%20meaningful%20asides%20that%20constitute%20a%20commentary%20on%20the%20realities%20of%20the%20times%20that%20we%20live%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20if%20one%20were%20to%20miss%20these%20piercing%20truths%20about%20shaking%20off%20the%20yoke%20of%20foreign%20rule%2C%20the%20pursuit%20of%20principles%20in%20the%20face%20of%20grave%20provocations%20and%20the%20dichotomy%20of%20power%20and%20duty%2C%20Freedom%20at%20Midnight%20has%20enough%20to%20keep%20the%20audience%20invested%20in%20the%20unfolding%20of%20the%20dra