%22The%20national%20capital's%20AQI%20was%20recorded%20at%20409%20on%20Friday%2C%20with%20thick%20smog%20covering%20the%20city%3B%20Grap-III%20implemented%20in%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20region%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-aqi-at-severe-level-when-will-school-closures-odd-even-begin-124111500516_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Abuse%20Of%20Power%20Charge%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20%26quot%3BHave%20We%20Arrested%20Anyone%26quot%3B%20Counter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20termed%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20as%20a%20battle%20for%20development%20and%20criticised%20the%20previous%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20government%20for%20allegedly%20stalling%20projects%20and%20veering%20away%20from%20the%20ideological%20roots%20laid%20by%20Shiv%20Sena's%20founder%2C%20Bal%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20election%20is%20focused%20on%20local%20issues%20and%20development.%20We%20are%20fighting%20this%20election%20on%20the%20platform%20of%20development%2C%20and%20today%2C%20the%20people%20are%20so%20confident%20that%20they%20say%2C%20'This%20is%20our%20government%3B%20this%20is%20our%20Chief%20Minister'.%20There%20is%20a%20strong%20connection%2C%20and%20the%20people%20are%20determined%20to%20bring%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%20back%20to%20power%20in%20this%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shinde%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20alleged%20that%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20-%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20the%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20factions%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20his%20deputy%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20-%20has%20restored%20momentum%20to%20projects%20that%20the%20previous%20Mahavikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20government%20-%20an%20alliance%20which%20includes%20the%20Congress%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%2C%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20faction%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20-%20stalled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20while%20the%20Mahavikas%20Aghadi%20government%20held%20power%2C%20they%20put%20a%20hold%20on%20numerous%20projects%2C%20slowed%20things%20down%2C%20and%20set%20up%20roadblocks.%20I%20won't%20list%20all%20the%20projects%20now%2C%20but%20there%20were%20many%20significant%20ones%20across%20Mumbai%2C%20including%20the%20Atal%20Setu%2C%20Coastal%20Road%2C%20and%20the%20Metro.%20Projects%20that%20extended%20beyond%20Mumbai%2C%20like%20the%20Nagpur-Mumbai%20expressway%2C%20initiatives%20for%20Maharashtra's%20farmers%2C%20the%20Marathwada%20Water%20Grid%2C%20and%20river-linking%20projects%20-%20all%20of%20these%20were%20hindered.%20When%20our%20government%20took%20office%2C%20we%20removed%20those%20roadblocks%2C%20work%20resumed%2C%20and%20development%20is%20now%20visible%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Shinde%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Betrayed%20Bal%20Thackeray'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20for%20the%20288-member%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20are%20set%20to%20take%20place%20on%20November%2020%2C%20while%20the%20counting%20will%20take%20place%20three%20days%20later.%20The%202019%20polls%20saw%20the%20BJP%20with%20105%20seats%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20with%2056%2C%20and%20Congress%20securing%2044.%20The%20MVA%20alliance%20gained%20momentum%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20winning%2030%20out%20of%2048%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Mahayuti%20coalition%20claimed%2017%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20projects%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcommon%20man's%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20insisting%20that%20he%20remains%20grounded%20and%20accessible%2C%20contrasting%20his%20style%20with%20that%20of%20the%20previous%20Maharashtra%20government.%20%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20Varsha%20(Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister's%20official%20residence)%20was%20restricted%3B%20everyone%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20come%20in.%20Today%2C%20everyone%20is%20coming%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20accused%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20of%20betraying%20Sena%20patriarch%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray's%20ideology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20worker%2C%20my%20mission%20is%20to%20advance%20this%20state.%20Uddhav%20ji%20abandoned%20the%20ideology%20of%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray%2C%20he%20left%20those%20principles%20behind%2C%20betrayed%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20betrayed%20the%20public%20trust.%20The%20mandate%20the%20people%20gave%20to%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20alliance%20was%20broken%20by%20Uddhav%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shinde%20alleged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Maratha%20Reservation%20Issue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20also%20addressed%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20issue%2C%20a%20topic%20that%20has%20sparked%20protests%20and%20hurt%20the%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20this%20year.%20The%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20in%20February%20this%20year%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20bill%20providing%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20the%20Maratha%20community%20in%20education%20and%20government%20jobs.%20However%2C%20protesters%20are%20demanding%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20under%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20gave%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20what%20should%20have%20been%20granted%20long%20ago.%20Previous%20governments%20used%20the%20Maratha%20community%20without%20delivering%20real%20benefits.%20When%20I%20became%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20and%20even%20during%20Devendra%20ji's%20term%2C%20we%20introduced%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20quota%20and%20upheld%20it%20in%20the%20High%20Court.%20But%20then%20the%20MVA%20government%20took%20over%20and%20failed%20to%20protect%20it.%20When%20we%20returned%2C%20we%20reinstated%20that%2010%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shinde%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20two%20other%20fronts%2C%20our%20government%20has%20worked%20to%20issue%20certificates%20and%20established%20the%20Justice%20Shinde%20Committee%20and%20the%20Backward%20Commission%2C%20which%20we%20reconstituted.%20We%20have%20gathered%20data%20proving%20social%20and%20educational%20backwardness%20per%20Supreme%20Court%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbuse%20Of%20Power%20Allegations%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20his%20government%20against%20accusations%20of%20misusing%20agencies%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20was%20quick%20to%20point%20fingers%20at%20the%20previous%20MVA%20administration%2C%20which%20he%20claimed%20had%20targeted%20political%20opponents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20were%20arrested%20for%20reciting%20the%20Hanuman%20Chalisa%2C%20including%20women%20and%20journalists.%20Have%20we%20jailed%20anyone%20unfairly%3F%20After%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20we%20corrected%20course%20where%20needed.%20Over%20the%20past%20four%20months%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20spread%20false%20narratives%2C%20claiming%20constitutional%20changes%20or%20that%20reservations%20will%20disappear.%20They've%20tried%20to%20intimidate%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%2C%20tribals%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20other%20minorities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shinde%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20administration%2C%20he%20maintained%2C%20is%20working%20to%20uplift%20these%20communities%20by%20%26quot%3Bbringing%20the%20Dalit%20and%20backward%20class%20to%20the%20mainstream.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731645720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fl3dhh0dg_eknath-shinde-ndtv-exclusive-_625x300_15_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-elections-uddhav-thackeray-abandoned-bal-thackerays-ideology-eknath-shinde-to-ndtv-7023544%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20criticised%20the%20previous%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20government%20for%20allegedly%20stalling%20projects%20and%20veering%20away%20from%20the%20ideological%20roots%20laid%20by%20Shiv%20Sena's%20founder%2C%20Bal%20Thackeray.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-elections-uddhav-thackeray-abandoned-bal-thackerays-ideology-eknath-shinde-to-ndtv-7023544%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Midnight%20bullock%20cart%20races%20on%20UP%20highway%20bring%20chaos%2C%20cruelty%20%26amp%3B%20crashes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731645527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115323170%2Cimgsize-870010.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmeerut%2Fmidnight-bullock-cart-races-on-uttar-pradesh-highway-bring-chaos-cruelty-crashes%2Farticleshow%2F115323128.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SANDEEP%20RAI%20AND%20KRISHNA%20CHAUDHARY%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%2C%20Anti-Vaccine%20Activist%20Who%20Is%20Now%20US%20Health%20Secretary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20appointed%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%2C%20an%20environmental%20advocate%20and%20vaccine%20sceptic%2C%20to%20lead%20the%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20(HHS).%20Mr%20Kennedy%2C%20who%20dropped%20his%20independent%20presidential%20campaign%20in%20August%20and%20endorsed%20Trump%2C%20has%20expressed%20his%20commitment%20to%20prioritising%20the%20fight%20against%20chronic%20diseases.%20His%20stance%20on%20vaccines%2C%20however%2C%20sets%20him%20apart%20from%20previous%20HHS%20leaders.%20Mr%20Kennedy%20has%20frequently%20challenged%20vaccine%20mandates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKennedy%20will%20restore%20these%20agencies%20to%20the%20traditions%20of%20gold%20standard%20scientific%20research%2C%20and%20beacons%20of%20transparency%2C%20to%20end%20the%20chronic%20disease%20epidemic%2C%20and%20to%20Make%20America%20Great%20and%20Healthy%20Again!%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-tracker-robert-f-kennedy-jr-anti-vaccine-activist-named-head-to-us-health-department-7022811%C2%A0%5C%22%3ETrump%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20was%20born%20on%20January%2017%2C%201954%2C%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20He%20is%20the%20third%20of%20eleven%20children%20of%20former%20US%20Attorney%20General%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20and%20Ethel%20Skakel%20Kennedy%2C%20and%20the%20nephew%20of%20former%20President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy.%20Both%20his%20father%20and%20uncle%20were%20assassinated%20in%20the%201960s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20studied%20at%20Harvard%20University%2C%20attended%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20and%20earned%20a%20law%20degree%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia.%20Later%2C%20he%20completed%20a%20Master's%20Degree%20in%20Environmental%20Law%20from%20Pace%20University%20School%20of%20Law%2C%20where%20he%20co-founded%20the%20Environmental%20Litigation%20Clinic%20and%20served%20on%20the%20faculty%20for%20over%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201980s%2C%20Mr%20Kennedy%20founded%20the%20Waterkeeper%20Alliance%2C%20an%20organisation%20focused%20on%20clean%20water%20advocacy%2C%20where%20he%20worked%20as%20chairman%20and%20attorney.%20His%20work%20to%20restore%20New%20York's%20Hudson%20River%20earned%20him%20the%20title%20%26quot%3BHero%20for%20the%20Planet%26quot%3B%20from%20TIME%20Magazine%20and%20helped%20create%20over%20300%20similar%20Waterkeeper%20groups%20worldwide.%20He%20also%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20New%20York%20City%20watershed%20agreement%2C%20now%20viewed%20as%20a%20global%20example%20of%20sustainable%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kennedy%20founded%20Children's%20Health%20Defense%20to%20address%20their%20health%20issues%20and%20harmful%20exposures%2C%20serving%20as%20chairman%20and%20lead%20counsel.%20While%20claiming%20to%20support%20vaccine%20safety%2C%20he%20has%20also%20been%20found%20spreading%20false%20theories%2C%20such%20as%20vaccines%20causing%20autism%20and%20COVID-19%20being%20targeted%20at%20specific%20ethnic%20groups.%20Before%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20Mr%20Kennedy%20was%20already%20leading%20campaigns%20against%20vaccines%20and%20collaborating%20with%20anti-vaccine%20groups.%20His%20organisation%20has%20also%20filed%20lawsuits%20against%20news%20outlets%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20bias%20against%20anti-vaccine%20views.%20Studies%20show%20his%20Twitter%20account%20was%20a%20major%20source%20of%20vaccine%20misinformation.%20Mr%20Kennedy%20has%20also%20met%20with%20anti-vaccine%20activists%20and%20supported%20anti-vaccine%20literature%2C%20despite%20evidence%20that%20vaccines%20are%20safe%20and%20necessary%20for%20public%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Mr%20Kennedy's%20legal%20wins%20include%20cases%20against%20Monsanto%20in%202018%20and%20DuPont%20in%202019%20for%20contamination%2C%20which%20inspired%20the%20movie%20Dark%20Waters.%20He%20has%20also%20advocated%20for%20Indigenous%20groups%20in%20North%20and%20South%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kennedy%20has%20authored%20several%20books%2C%20including%20bestsellers%20Crimes%20Against%20Nature%20(2005)%20and%20The%20Real%20Anthony%20Fauci%20(2021).%20He%20has%20also%20written%20children's%20books%20on%20American%20history%20and%20Saint%20Francis%20of%20Assisi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%20is%20married%20to%20actress%20Cheryl%20Hines%20and%20has%20seven%20children%20from%20three%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731645240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fd2ml1er_robert-f-kennedy-jr-afp_625x300_15_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Frobert-f-kennedy-jr-anti-vaccine-activist-who-is-now-us-health-secretary-7023554%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20appointed%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%2C%20an%20environmental%20advocate%20and%20vaccine%20sceptic%2C%20to%20lead%20the%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20(HHS).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Frobert-f-kennedy-jr-anti-vaccine-activist-who-is-now-us-health-secretary-7023554%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20vs%20India%20A%20Practice%20Match%3A%20Kohli%20Gone%20For%2015%2C%20Pant%20Only%20Made...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20behind-closed-doors%20match%2C%20India%20and%20India%20A%20squared%20off%20ahead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Border%20Gavaskar%20Trophy.%20The%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20scheduled%20the%203-day%20match%20starting%20Friday%2C%20though%20barred%20fans%20from%20attending%20the%20fixture%20at%20WACA.%20On%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20the%20warm-up%20game%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20worrying%20news%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20talismanic%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20yet%20again%20failed%20to%20produce%20an%20upturn%20in%20his%20form.%20Even%20India's%20hero%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%200-3%20whitewash%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20dismisse