tractions%20and%20theme%20parks%20open%20in%20the%20area%2C%20it's%20%26quot%3Bgenerally%20beneficial%26quot%3B%20for%20Disney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223984%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cinderella's%20Castle%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20in%20Florida.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67368630fa0140cdd563a3e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECinderella's%20Castle%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20in%20Florida.%3Cp%3EArturo%20Holmes%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Disney%20Dreamers%20Academy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDennis%20Speigel%2C%20founder%20of%20International%20Theme%20Park%20Services%2C%20Inc.%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Epic%20Universe's%20opening%20will%20likely%20bring%20more%20foot%20traffic%20to%20Central%20Florida%2C%20which%20can%20benefit%20the%20local%20attractions%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20length%20of%20stay%20for%20the%20tourists%20in%20Florida%20is%20going%20to%20increase%20dramatically%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20are%20going%20to%20load%20another%20day%20or%20a%20day%20and%20a%20half%20during%20their%20visit%20because%20there's%20more%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Disney%20and%20Universal%20Orlando%20Resort%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENBCUniversal%20first%20announced%20Epic%20Universe%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20new%20park%20represents%20the%20single-largest%20investment%20Comcast%20NBCUniversal%20has%20made%20in%20its%20theme%20park%20business%20and%20in%20Florida%20overall%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20L.%20Roberts%2C%20chief%20executive%20of%20Comcast%20Corporation%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BIt%20reflects%20the%20tremendous%20excitement%20we%20have%20for%20the%20future%20of%20our%20theme%20park%20business%20and%20for%20our%20entire%20company's%20future%20in%20Florida.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Illustration%20of%20Universal%20Orlando%20Resort's%20Epic%20Universe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673685cbfa0140cdd563a3dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIllustration%20of%20Universal%20Orlando%20Resort's%20Epic%20Universe.%3Cp%3EUniversal%20Orlando%20Resort%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUniversal%20Orlando%20Resort%20was%20the%20company's%20oldest%20park%20in%201990%2C%20followed%20by%20Islands%20of%20Adventure%20in%201999%20and%20Volcano%20Bay%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Epic%20Universe%2C%20guests%20will%20get%20the%20opportunity%20to%20explore%20five%20worlds%3A%20Super%20Nintendo%20World%2C%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Magic%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%20franchise%2C%20the%20Isle%20of%20Berk%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Train%20Your%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20franchise%2C%20Dark%20Universe%20featuring%20monsters%20from%20classic%20horror%20films%2C%20and%20Celestial%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Disney%20shocked%20fans%20in%20August%20when%20Experiences%20Chairman%20Josh%20D'Amaro%20said%20its%20parks%20were%20also%20expanding.%20The%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20Central%20Florida%20Tourism%20Oversight%20District's%20board%20of%20supervisors%20approved%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesantis-disney-development-deal-fifth-gate-new-theme-park-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2417%20billion%20development%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Disney%20two%20months%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Disney%20won't%20build%20a%20separate%20theme%20park%2C%20the%20entertainment%20giant%20will%20add%20new%20areas%20to%20its%20existing%20properties.%20Magic%20Kingdom%20will%20become%20home%20to%20a%20land%20dedicated%20to%20Disney%20villains%20and%20another%20based%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BCars%26quot%3B%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney's%20Animal%20Kingdom%20will%20introduce%20a%20new%20land%20called%20Pueblo%20Esperanza%2C%20which%20will%20have%20attractions%20based%20on%20the%202021%20film%20%26quot%3BEncanto%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3BIndiana%20Jones%26quot%3B%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Disney's%20Hollywood%20Studios%2C%20guests%20will%20explore%20a%20new%20land%20based%20on%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3BMonsters%2C%20Inc%26quot%3B%20films.%20Finally%2C%20Disneyland%20Resort's%20Avenger's%20campus%20will%20expand%20and%20an%20attraction%20related%20to%20director%20James%20Cameron's%20%26quot%3BAvatar%26quot%3B%20series%20will%20arrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Thursday's%20earnings%20report%2C%20Disney%20expects%20its%20Experiences%20segment's%20operating%20income%20to%20grow%206%25%20to%208%25%20compared%20to%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepic-universes-opening-could-benefit-walt-disney-world-cfo-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731629998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67366d5eede4eeae3927b679%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepic-universes-opening-could-benefit-walt-disney-world-cfo-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Epic%20Universe's%20arrival%20in%20Orlando%20could%20benefit%20its%20competitor%2C%20Walt%20Disney%20World%2C%20the%20company's%20CFO%20Hugh%20Johnston%20said%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepic-universes-opening-could-benefit-walt-disney-world-cfo-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20started%20using%20dating%20apps%20in%20my%2050s%20and%20quickly%20grew%20frustrated.%20Coming%20up%20with%20the%20'burned%20haystack'%20dating%20method%20helped.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22996%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jennie%20Young%20sitting%20outside%20on%20stairs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67298371192f525898560950%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22747%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJennie%20Young%20created%20the%20Burned%20Haystack%20Dating%20Method.%3Cp%3EJennie%20Young%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAt%2050%2C%20Jennie%20Young%20started%20using%20several%20dating%20apps%20and%20felt%20that%20they%20were%20all%20toxic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Burned%20Haystack%20Dating%20Method%20began%20as%20an%20academic%20project%20and%20now%20has%20a%20Facebook%20group%20with%20over%20128%2C000%20members.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYoung%2C%20a%20college%20professor%2C%20has%20advice%20for%20the%20companies%20behind%20dating%20apps.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJennie%20Young%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20rhetoric%20and%20women%2Fgender%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Green%20Bay.%20In%20February%202023%2C%20she%20started%20a%20Facebook%20group%20for%20the%20Burned%20Haystack%20Dating%20Method.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20knew%20what%20to%20expect%20when%20I%20downloaded%20my%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-dating-startups-and-apps-disrupting-the-industry-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edating%20app%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%2050%2C%20had%20been%20divorced%20for%2010%20years%2C%20and%20had%20just%20gotten%20out%20of%20a%20long-term%20relationship.%20As%20someone%20who's%20generally%20tuned%20in%20to%20pop%20culture%20and%20social%20media%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20prepared%20for%20what%20I%20would%20encounter.%20And%2C%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20I%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20wasn't%20prepared%20for%20was%20the%20size%20or%20extent%20of%20the%20problem%20women%20were%20facing%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-is-a-dating-app-remote-work-online-romance-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooking%20for%20love%20online.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20weren't%20just%20a%20few%20men%20acting%20badly%20whom%20I%20could%20quickly%20dispatch.%20It%20was%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20toxicity.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20bad%20actors%2C%20and%20the%20behavior%20wasn't%20just%20annoying%3B%20it%20was%20deeply%20problematic.%20It%20seemed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftinder-swipe-right-inventor-how-he-came-up-with-it-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswiping%20left%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20make%20a%20difference%3B%20they'd%20just%20show%20up%20in%20my%20matches%20again%20a%20few%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20frustration%20wasn't%20unique.%20Articles%20from%202024%20alone%20included%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20Not%20You%3A%20Dating%20Apps%20are%20Getting%20Worse%26quot%3B%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3B%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20is%20Sick%20of%20Swiping%3A%20Dating%20Apps%20are%20Falling%20Back%20to%20Earth%26quot%3B%20in%20The%20Atlantic%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BWhy%20Gen%20Z%20is%20Ditching%20Dating%20Apps%26quot%3B%20in%20Time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20from%20Match%20to%20Bumble%20to%20Tinder%20to%20Hinge%20and%20encountered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-dating-trend-online-apps-friends-romantic-partners-relationships-2023-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520interviews%2520conducted%2520for%2520our%2Cyear%252Dold%2520woman%2520told%2520us.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20same%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%20ad%20infinitum.%20I%20felt%20frustrated%20and%20quickly%20realized%20it%20was%20not%20just%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5c6f459-2f3e-4795-9196-b81ba18c36d3%5C%22%3EI%20developed%20my%20own%20method%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20months%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20make%20it%20an%20academic%20project.%20I'm%20a%20professor%20of%20rhetoric%20and%20women%2Fgender%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Green%20Bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20understanding%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fharvard-edx-rhetoric-persuasive-writing-public-speaking-free-online-course-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erhetoric%3C%2Fa%3E%20allows%20me%20to%20quickly%20parse%20text%20and%20read%20between%20the%20lines%20to%20determine%20what%20people%20are%20revealing%20without%20intending%20to%2C%20and%20a%20solid%20grounding%20in%20feminism%20helps%20me%20recognize%20the%20sometimes%20subtle%20flags%20of%20sexism%20and%20aggression%20that%20women%20encounter%20frequently%20on%20dating%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20evolved%20into%20a%20new%20dating%20method%20that%20I%20named%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-apps-new-method-online-burned-haystack-jennie-young-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurned%20Haystack%20Dating%20Method.%3C%2Fa%3E%20My%20method%20encourages%20daters%20to%20filter%20out%20time%20wasters%20and%20red%20flags%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20November%2013%2C%20there%20were%20over%20128%2C000%20women%2Fnonbinary%20people%20in%20my%20private%20Facebook%20group%20and%2060%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20to%20share%20the%20method%20on%20social%20media%20because%20it's%20free.%20Accessibility%20was%20important%20to%20me%20from%20the%20beginning%3B%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20monetize%20the%20information%20by%20keeping%20it%20behind%20a%20paywall%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20charge%20women%20for%20consultation%20or%20%26quot%3Bcoaching.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little%20over%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20after%20creating%20the%20method%20and%20developing%20a%20following%2C%20I've%20learned%20a%20few%20things%20that%20I%20feel%20would%20keep%20daters%20happier%20with%20the%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2222981425-e194-4e8b-9ab6-be45e84acd9d%5C%22%3EWomen%20feel%20like%20their%20preferences%20are%20being%20ignored%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20typical%20scenario%20I've%20experienced%2C%20and%20that%20has%20been%20repeated%20to%20me%20on%20several%20occasions%20by%20women%20who%20have%20spent%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforever-alone-staying-single-done-with-dating-apps-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20dating%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20A%20woman%20is%20excited%20to%20set%20up%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-dating-app-dm-era-of-swipe-fatigue-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20dating%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20profile.%20She%20carefully%20selects%20her%20prompts%2C%20writes%20thoughtful%20responses%2C%20and%20curates%20her%20pictures.%20She%20sets%20boundaries%20around%20things%20like%20age%2C%20geography%2C%20marital%20status%2C%20political%20orientation%2C%20and%20lifestyle%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20me%20and%20many%20of%20those%20I've%20spoken%20to%2C%20the%20apps%20appear%20to%20honor%20almost%20none%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20told%20me%20she%20had%20specified%20that%20she%20was%20looking%20for%20a%2040-to-45-year-old%20politically%20liberal%20nonsmoker%20within%2050%20miles%20of%20her%20home.%20This%20didn't%20stop%20the%20app%20she%20was%20using%20from%20showing%20her%20a%20full%20line-up%20of%2060-year-old%20chain%20smokers%20from%20three%20hours%20away.%20So%20she%20swiped%20left%2C%20but%20the%20next%20matches%20were%20even%20worse%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20the%20same%20men%20she%20swiped%20left%20on%20originally%20reappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20women%20have%20mentioned%20reporting%20toxic%20behavior%20directly%20to%20dating%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-favorite-dating-app-fatigue-tokyo-america-birth-rate-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDating%20app%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecompanies%20are%20not%20responsible%20for%20fixing%20the%20users%2C%20nor%20is%20that%20even%20possible%2C%20but%20there%20are%20things%20I%20feel%20they%20could%20do%20better%20Here%20are%20three%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EListen%20to%20users%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Honor%20the%20boundaries%20articulated.%20If%20someone%20swipes%20left%2C%20don't%20show%20the%20same%20person%20to%20them%20again.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20anyone%20who%20meets%20the%20said%20criteria%2C%20then%20simply%20say%20that.%20Leave%20it%20up%20to%20the%20individual%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20expand%20their%20filters%20or%20just%20wait.%20They're%20all%20adults.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20a%20better%20job%20of%20screening%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20AI%20tools%20can%20now%20screen%20for%20tone%20problems%20such%20as%20aggression.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20the%20bad%20actors%20out%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20reports%20are%20made%20regarding%20toxicity%2C%20aggression%2C%20and%20deceit%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20just%20means%20lying%20about%20age%20or%20marital%20status%20%E2%80%94%20verify%20and%20remove%20the%20offenders.%20Users%20also%20need%20to%20be%20more%20vigilant%20about%20reporting%20bad%20behavior%20to%20the%20apps%2C%20as%20many%20of%20the%20companies%20will%20take%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20remove%20the%20profile.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20changes%20won't%20solve%20the%20larger%20cultural%20problems%20women%20face%20in%20the%20dating%20market%2C%20but%20implementing%20them%20could%20improve%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-dating-apps-interested-men-non-monogamous-open-relationships-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edating%20app%20experience%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhile%20we%20continue%20to%20address%20the%20problems%20in%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20it%20would%20improve%20things%20for%20daters%2C%20it's%20not%20likely%20it%20would%20improve%20things%20financially%20for%20the%20apps.%20Last%20month%2C%20Albert%20Fox%20Cahn%2C%20a%20journalist%2C%20wrote%20in%20BI%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-apps-find-love-romance-online-tinder-match-total-scam-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapps%20face%20a%20problem%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20popularity%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20turns%20out%20dating%20apps%20face%20a%20unique%20barrier%20to%20success%3A%20The%20more%20effective%20your%20app%20is%2C%20the%20less%20profitable%20it%20becomes.%20People%20pay%20to%20find%20a%20partner%2C%20and%20once%20you%20find%20one%2C%20the%20app%20loses%20your%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Cahn%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20dating%20apps%20and%20singles%20face%20a%20conflicting%20definition%20of%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20representative%20from%20Match%20Group.%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20Tinder%20and%20Hinge%2C%20told%20BI%20they%20have%20made%20investments%20to%20improve%20both%20their%20automated%20and%20manual%20moderation%20and%20review%20tools.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BThese%20tools%20include%20automatic%20scans%20of%20profiles%20for%20red-flag%20language%20and%20images%2C%20manual%20reviews%20of%20suspicious%20profiles%2C%20activity%2C%20and%20user%20generated%20reports%2C%20as%20well%20as%20blocking%20email%20addresses%2C%20phone%20numbers%20and%20other%20identifiers%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Match%20Group.%20respresentive%20said.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20representative%20said%20the%20company%20spends%20%24125%20million%20a%20year%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Btrust%20and%20safety%20teams%2C%20technology%2C%20partnerships%2C%20and%20initiatives%20and%20is%20focused%20on%20improving%20safety%20across%20the%20Match%20Group%20portfolio.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAccording%20to%20Bumble%2C%20the%20app%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ematches%20people%20who%20have%20mutually%20swiped%20on%20each%20other.%20The%20platform%20is%20set%20up%20so%20that%20women%20make%20the%20first%20move%2C%20and%20they%20can%20reply%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20or%20the%20match%20expires.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBumble%20said%20that%20anyone%20who%20experiences%20harassment%20is%20encouraged%20to%20use%20the%20app's%20%26quot%3BBlock%20and%20Report%26quot%3B%20system.%20Bumble%20also%20said%20the%20app%20is%20using%20automated%20and%20AI-based%20technology%20to%20identify%20potential%20violations%20before%20members%20even%20report%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-professor-burned-haystack-online-dating-method-apps-match-bumble-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731629641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6729838688cea3ba1c1e4344%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-professor-burned-haystack-online-dating-method-apps-match-bumble-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jennie%20Young%20recognizes%20that%20dating%20app%20companies%20are%20not%20responsible%20for%20fixing%20bad%20users%2C%20but%20says%20there%20are%20things%20they%20could%20do%20better.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jennie%20Young)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-professor-burned-haystack-online-dating-method-apps-match-bumble-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UN%20climate%20talks%20'no%20longer%20fit%20for%20purpose'%20say%20key%20experts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731629461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fcd36%2Flive%2F77ac9db0-a2e0-11ef-bf71-6ff17bcfa8a9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%