quot%3BPeople%20are%20getting%20really%20into%20'art%20toys'%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20kind%20of%20a%20mix%20of%20art%2C%20fashion%2C%20and%20pop%20culture%20all%20rolled%20into%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20Kanaprach%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20lot%20of%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Zers%2C%20these%20aren't%20just%20toys.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey're%20seen%20as%20little%20pieces%20of%20art%20or%20cool%20design%20items%20that%20look%20great%20in%20their%20homes.%20It's%20like%20adding%20a%20bit%20of%20personality%20and%20style%20to%20their%20space%2C%20not%20just%20something%20to%20play%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%2C%20a%20representative%20from%20Pop%20Mart%20said%20that%20Labubu%20has%20gained%20a%20strong%20global%20fan%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20become%20more%20than%20just%20a%20collectible%E2%80%94it's%20a%20way%20for%20people%20to%20express%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237e61215-fe06-4fde-a209-d7d009d9b1f9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollectors%20say%20Labubu%20is%20worth%20the%20snaking%20lines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sim%20Pei%20Yi%20heard%20from%20a%20group%20chat%20that%20Labubu%20toys%20were%20being%20restocked%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20she%20rushed%20to%20a%20Singapore%20Pop%20Mart%20to%20join%20a%20snaking%20line%20with%20her%20colleague%20during%20lunchtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20'FOMO'%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sim%2C%2031%2C%20who%20owns%20around%20six%20Labubu%20toys.%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20is%20getting%20Labubu.%20You%20will%20also%20want%20to%20have%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20girl%20holding%20her%20Labubu%20toys%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67331f17192f52589857c911%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAna%20Gonzales%20said%20she's%20spent