ww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Esavings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20that%20I%20could%20not%20only%20capitalize%20on%20my%20skills%20(such%20as%20writing%2C%20public%20speaking%2C%20and%20marketing)%20to%20take%20on%20side%20work%20as%20a%20freelancer%2C%20consultant%2C%20and%20workshop%20teacher%20but%20that%20I%20could%20use%20my%20free%20time%20on%20the%20weekends%20to%20make%20money%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20start%20a%20business%20in%20the%20wedding%20industry%20as%20a%20bridesmaid%20for%20hire%20so%20that%20it%20wouldn't%20interfere%20with%20my%20full-time%20job%20during%20the%20week%20and%20brought%20in%20additional%20income%20through%20that%20stream.%20I%20also%20created%20profiles%20on%20babysitting%20websites%C2%A0and%20helped%20friends%20sell%20their%20clothes%20and%20furniture%20when%20they%20moved%2C%20and%20took%20a%20fee%20from%20sales%20that%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20shifting%20how%20I%20spent%20my%20weekends%2C%20from%20using%20the%20time%20to%20relax%20and%20socialize%20to%20finding%20ways%20to%20make%20money%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20earn%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20extra%20every%20month%20through%20various%20side%20hustles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20in%20handy%20when%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20my%20full-time%20job%20in%202015.%20When%20I%20lost%20that%20steady%20paycheck%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20build%20up%20my%20wedding%20business%20and%20leverage%20some%20of%20the%20other%20side%20hustles%20to%20bring%20in%20more%20money%20than%20I%20was%20making%20from%20just%20the%20full-time%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20to%20make%20extra%20cash%20on%20the%20weekend%2C%20here%20are%20five%20side%20hustles%20you%20can%20try%20that%20may%20help%20you%20make%20more%20money%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Work%20events%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20steady%20work%2C%20grab%20a%20job%20in%20the%20event%20industry%2C%20since%20the%20weekends%20are%20when%20many%20people%20throw%20parties%2C%20celebrations%2C%20and%20weddings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20identify%20what%20skills%20you%20have%20that%20could%20be%20of%20value%20in%20the%20event%20industry.%20Use%20websites%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gigsalad.com%5C%22%3EGigSalad%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thumbtack.com%5C%22%3EThumbtack%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20browse%20common%20vendors%20that%20people%20hire%20for%20parties%20and%20see%20what%20passions%20you%20have%20that%20could%20be%20listed%20for%20hire%20on%20those%20types%20of%20websites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20you're%20someone%20with%20a%20passion%20or%20hobby%2C%20turn%20that%20into%20an%20offered%20service%20(floral%20design%2C%20DJ%2C%20photographer%2C%20etc.)%20or%20join%20an%20existing%20company%20that%20offers%20those%20services%20as%20their%20weekend%20assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20experience%20in%20the%20food%20services%20industry%20(as%20a%20server%20or%20a%20hostess)%2C%20you%20can%20also%20secure%20a%20job%20working%20for%20a%20caterer%20as%20a%20cater-waiter.%20These%20jobs%20typically%20pay%20hourly%20and%20are%20a%20great%20way%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house%20on%20a%20weekend%20and%20work%20as%20a%20food%20server%20at%20a%20big%20celebration.%20You%20can%20find%20a%20list%20of%20local%20opportunities%20on%20job%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Give%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20local%3Cstrong%3E%20tours%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20college%2C%20I%20took%20a%20weekend%20job%20as%20a%20campus%20tour%20guide.%20Each%20tour%20took%20around%20three%20hours%20and%20I'd%20start%20the%20week%20off%20with%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20in%20my%20pocket%20from%20that%20gig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20extroverted%2C%20enjoy%20working%20with%20groups%20of%20people%2C%20and%20can%20retain%20information%20easily%2C%20you%20can%20find%20a%20weekend%20job%20as%20a%20local%20tour%20guide.%20Cities%20that%20are%20popular%20tourist%20destinations%20offer%20a%20variety%20of%20tours%20that%20focus%20on%20landmarks%2C%20food%2C%20famous%20TV%20shows%2C%20and%20more.%20You%20can%20browse%20local%20event%20websites%20to%20see%20what%20tours%20are%20offered%20and%20contact%20those%20companies%20to%20see%20if%20they%20are%20hiring%20tour%20assistants%20so%20you%20can%20get%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20consider%20creating%20profiles%20on%20websites%20that%20offer%20tourists%20tours%20by%20locals%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toursbylocals.com%2F%3Fgclid%3DCj0KCQjwpv2TBhDoARIsALBnVnlRwIEcghbb92FiRvwWq-QbESwLM55PFuu9DIf-HxDti7kJoKbWi0MaAs9UEALw_wcB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETours%20By%20Locals%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.withlocals.com%2F%3Fgclid%3DCj0KCQjwpv2TBhDoARIsALBnVnkmNcEs0y__DzPaRLg___EcuXo-d0V7KvqA-XxtI-HnBsf9ZWcSnwYaAg3eEALw_wcB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWith%20Locals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20notice%20a%20specific%20kind%20of%20tour%20that%20you%20believe%20would%20attract%20customers%20on%20a%20weekend%2C%20consider%20starting%20it%20yourself.%20You%20can%20advertise%20your%20tour%20on%20websites%20that%20tourists%20visit%20to%20find%20local%20activities%2C%20like%20%3Cspan%3EAirbnb%20Experiences%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yelp.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYelp%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20tour%20guide%2C%20your%20weekend%20pay%20can%20be%20determined%20by%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20how%20many%20people%20take%20your%20tour%2C%20whether%20you're%20receiving%20an%20hourly%20salary%2C%20and%20how%20much%20cash%20you%20make%20in%20tips.%20If%20you%20run%20your%20own%20tour%20company%20and%20charge%20%2450%20a%20tour%2C%20you'd%20need%20to%20book%2020%20spots%20on%20Saturday%20and%2020%20on%20Sunday%20to%20make%20%242%2C000%20in%20potential%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Help%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20random%20tasks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20early%2020s%2C%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20extra%20cash%20on%20the%20weekends%20but%20didn't%20want%20to%20commit%20to%20a%20regular%20job%2C%20I%20put%20myself%20on%20task-based%20websites%20where%20people%20could%20hire%20me%20for%20one-off%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20use%20websites%20like%20%3Cspan%3ETaskRabbit%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20Thumbtack%2C%20you%20can%20offer%20your%20time%2C%20resources%2C%20or%20skills%20to%20people%20who%20need%20them.%20In%20one%20weekend%2C%20you%20can%20help%20someone%20move%2C%20build%20their%20furniture%2C%20paint%20their%20apartment%2C%20or%20even%20take%20on%20tasks%20as%20their%20virtual%20assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20money%20you%20can%20make%20through%20this%20side%20hustle%20does%20vary%20based%20on%20how%20much%20you%20charge%20and%20how%20many%20hours%20on%20the%20weekend%20you%20work.%20However%2C%20you%20can%20set%20your%20rate%20for%20different%20tasks%20that%20you're%20willing%20to%20do%20or%20just%20set%20a%20general%20hourly%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Become%3Cstrong%3E%20a%20sitter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20City%20and%20needed%20to%20supplement%20my%20income%2C%20I%20took%20on%20weekend%20babysitting%20jobs.%20I%20created%20a%20profile%20on%20a%20local%20babysitting%20website%2C%20posted%20flyers%20in%20my%20apartment%20building%2C%20and%20shared%20the%20word%20with%20my%20friends.%20It%20helped%20me%20bring%20in%20an%20extra%20%241%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20addition%20to%20babysitting%2C%20you%20can%20also%20get%20paid%20to%20house%20sit%20or%20pet%20sit%20for%20people%20when%20they%20go%20out%20of%20town.%20You%20can%20set%20up%20a%20profile%20on%20%3Cspan%3ERover%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhousesitter.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHouse%20Sitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20set%20your%20rate.%20If%20you're%20willing%20to%20let%20this%20side%20hustle%20carry%20over%20to%20during%20the%20week%20(especially%20if%20you%20work%20from%20home%20and%20can%20pet%20sit%20or%20house%20sit%20while%20working%20full-time)%2C%20you%20can%20really%20increase%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20you%20take%20in%20from%20these%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20with%20other%20service-based%20side%20hustles%2C%20you%20can%20set%20your%20rate%20and%20the%20locations%20you're%20willing%20to%20travel%20to%20for%20potential%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Sell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20people's%3Cstrong%3E%20things%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20can%20look%20around%20their%20living%20spaces%20and%20find%20a%20collection%20of%20items%20that%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20part%20with.%20Rather%20than%20tossing%20old%20electronics%20in%20the%20trash%20or%20leaving%20unused%20furniture%20in%20the%20garage%20to%20collect%20dust%2C%20you%20can%20create%20a%20side%20hustle%20out%20of%20selling%20your%20own%2C%20or%20other%20people's%2C%20unwanted%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20times%20a%20year%2C%20I%20gather%20a%20pile%20of%20items%20around%20my%20house%20and%20list%20them%20for%20sale%20on%20places%20like%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.offerup.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOfferup%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20also%20take%20clothing%2C%20accessories%2C%20and%20shoes%20to%20local%20thrift%20stores.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20make%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20off%20things%20around%20my%20house%20by%20doing%20very%20little%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20always%20do%20is%20take%20inventory%20of%20what%20I%20want%20to%20sell%20by%20listing%20the%20proper%20name%20of%20the%20item%2C%20writing%20out%20a%20detailed%20description%2C%20and%20assigning%20it%20a%20price%20based%20on%20its%20retail%20value%20and%20condition.%20Then%2C%20I%20use%20my%20phone%20to%20take%20photos%20of%20the%20item%20from%20different%20angles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20list%20each%20item%20on%20multiple%20platforms%20to%20get%20the%20products%20in%20front%20of%20more%20people.%20Some%20items%20sell%20within%20a%20day%20or%20two%2C%20and%20others%20take%20months%3B%20it%20just%20depends%20on%20the%20supply%20and%20demand%20of%20what%20you're%20selling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20really%20profit%20from%20this%20side%20hustle%2C%20offer%20to%20do%20this%20for%20other%20people%20so%20you%20have%20access%20to%20more%20items%20to%20list.%20Determine%20how%20much%20profit%20you'll%20take%20from%20each%20sale%2C%20and%20consider%20picking%20a%20specialty%20(like%20only%20selling%20electronics%20or%20furniture)%20so%20you%20can%20create%20a%20niche%20in%20the%20resale%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearn-thousands-simple-weekend-side-hustles-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731624961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62828be065d1770019e4883a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearn-thousands-simple-weekend-side-hustles-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you're%20looking%20to%20make%20some%20extra%20cash%20without%20taking%20on%20complex%20work%2C%20try%20taking%20on%20random%20tasks%20or%20selling%20other%20people's%20stuff%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearn-thousands-simple-weekend-side-hustles-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Musk%20supports%20Trump%20getting%20rid%20of%20EV%20tax%20credits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224224%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elon%20musk%20at%20trump%20rally%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672a9c0588cea3ba1c1e9420%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222608%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20still%20has%20a%20commanding%20lead%20in%20the%20US%20EV%20market%2C%20but%20competition%20is%20slowly%20catching%20up.%3Cp%3EANGELA%20WEISS%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20to%20benefit%20from%20any%20removal%20of%20consumer%20tax%20credits%20on%20electric%20vehicle%20purchases.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20could%20hurt%20competitors%20more%2C%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETesla%20makes%20a%20vast%20majority%20of%20EVs%20sold%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20its%20lead%20has%20started%20to%20slip%20slightly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20supports%20a%20Trump%20plan%20to%20end%20tax%20credits%20of%20up%20to%20%247%2C500%20for%20electric%20vehicle%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20might%20sound%20confusing%3A%20Why%20would%20the%20CEO%20of%20Tesla%20want%20to%20end%20a%20program%20that%20makes%20it%20cheaper%20for%20people%20to%20buy%20EVs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20according%20to%20Musk%2C%20it%20would%20devastate%20Tesla's%20rivals.%20And%20Tesla%20wants%20to%20keep%20its%20strong%20lead%20in%20the%20US%20EV%20market%2C%20which%20recently%20slipped%20under%2050%25%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20would%20be%20devastating%20for%20our%20competitors%20and%20for%20Tesla%20slightly%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20in%20a%20July%20earnings%20call%2C%20predicting%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20tax%20credits%20ending.%20%26quot%3BBut%20long%20term%20probably%20actually%20helps%20Tesla%2C%20would%20be%20my%20guess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Reuters%20reported%20that%20Trump%20plans%20to%20end%20the%20EV%20tax%20credit%2C%20with%20support%20from%20Tesla%20representatives.%20In%20a%20related%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Musk%20called%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bend%20all%20government%20subsidies%2C%20including%20those%20for%20EVs%2C%20oil%20and%20gas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20had%20a%20longer%20time%20than%20some%20of%20its%20rivals%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-list-government-subsidies-tesla-billions-spacex-solarcity-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefit%20from%20government%20subsidies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20market%20lead%20is%20well%20established%2C%20and%20it%20has%20led%20an%20EV%20pricing%20war%20that%20has%20squeezed%20its%20rivals%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20them%20to%20survive%20if%20consumer%20demand%20falls%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPut%20simply%3A%20Tesla%20wins%20if%20ending%20the%20tax%20credit%20pressures%20smaller%20rivals%20enough%20to%20stall%20their%20growth%20or%20even%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2291842e59-2373-4c08-abdd-17185b0bea0d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETesla%20sells%20more%20EVs%20than%20anyone%20else%2C%20and%20more%20profitably%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20Tesla%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigitalassets.tesla.com%2Ftesla-contents%2Fimage%2Fupload%2FIR%2FTSLA-Q3-2024-Update.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20pre-tax%20profit%20margin%20of%2018%25%2C%20well%20above%20the%20industry%20average%20of%20around%209%25.%20Ford%2C%20the%20only%20competitor%20to%20break%20out%20its%20EV-specific%20finances%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs201.q4cdn.com%2F693218008%2Ffiles%2Fdoc_financials%2F2024%2Fq3%2FPress-Release-Ford-2024-Q3-Earnings.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20-104%25%20margin%20for%20its%20Model%20e%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20many%20of%20Tesla's%20vehicles%20are%20also%20priced%20well%20below%20many%20competitors.%20The%20Model%203%20starts%20at%20%2442%2C490%20(after%20a%20cheaper%20option%20disappeared%20earlier%20this%20year).%20That's%20well%20below%20the%20average%20EV%20price%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20held%20steady%20at%20nearly%20%2457%2C000%20in%20October%2C%20according%20to%20Kelley%20Blue%20Book%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20juice%20sales%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-can-make-cars-cheaper-than-competitors-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20has%20drastically%20cut%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20many%20of%20its%20cars%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20instigating%20an%20industry-wide%20price%20war%20that%20has%20cut%20into%20its%20own%20margin%20in%20pursuit%20of%20maintaining%20its%20industry-leading%20market%20share.%20Of%20the%20nearly%20600%2C000%20EVs%20sold%20in%20the%20US%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coxautoinc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FQ2-2024-Kelley-Blue-Book-Electric-Vehicle-Sales-Report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehalf%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20made%20by%20Tesla.%20Ford%2C%20in%20second%20place%2C%20accounted%20for%20just%20over%207%25%20of%20EVs%20sold%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20losing%20the%20EV%20tax%20credit%20could%20also%20hurt%20some%20demand%20on%20the%20margins%20in%20the%20US%2C%20this%20will%20enable%20Tesla%20to%20further%20fend%20off%20competition%20from%20Detroit%20as%20pricing%2Fscale%2Fscope%20is%20an%20apples%20to%20oranges%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20auto%20industry%20once%20the%20EV%20tax%20credit%20disappears%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20Ives%2C%20a%20longtime%20bullish%20analyst%20at%20Wedbush%2C%20told%20clients%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6cefac7-9186-47f8-8f0a-f2fb65808785%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETesla%20is%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%20in%20building%20a%20US%20manufacturing%20presence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEliminating%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-state-electric-car-vehicle-tax-credits-rebates-qualify%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20tax%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20part%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%2C%20would%20need%20congressional%20approval.%20It's%20not%20yet%20clear%20if%20Trump%20and%20the%20incoming%20Republican-controlled%20Congress%20would%20also%20target%20other%20IRA%20tax%20incentives%2C%20like%20those%20supporting%20domestic%20manufacturing%20of%20cars%2C%20batteries%2C%20and%20other%20components.%20Competitors%20like%20BMW%2C%20Honda%2C%20and%20Hyundai%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2024%2F07%2F20%2Ftracking-the-ev-battery-factory-construction-boom-across-north-america%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraced%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20scale%20up%20factories%20state-side%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20those%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20been%20ahead%20of%20this%20curve%20in%20manufacturing%2C%20too%2C%20with%20six%20US%20factories%20churning%20out%20cars%20and%20batteries.%20That%20work%20has%20paid%20off%2C%20and%20many%20Tesla%20models%20are%20regularly%20named%20as%20the%20most%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cars.com%2Famerican-made-index%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican-made%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20compared%20to%20competitors%2C%20many%20of%20which%20rely%20on%20factories%20in%20Mexico.%20In%20fact%2C%20only%20one%20other%20American%20automaker%20even%20cracked%20the%20top%2010%20in%202024.%