e%20an%20influence%20on%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fimmunization%2Fwho-and-when%2Fmilitary-members%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%3C%2Fa%3E%20vaccine%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20stance%20has%20public%20health%20officials%20spooked%2C%20because%20part%20of%20what%20makes%20vaccination%20work%20so%20well%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20nearly%20everyone%20in%20our%20society%20does%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20very%20short%20memory%20of%20what%20it%20is%20like%20to%20hold%20a%20child%20who%20has%20been%20paralyzed%20with%20polio%2C%20or%20to%20comfort%20a%20mom%20who%20lost%20their%20kid%20from%20measles%2C%26quot%3B%20CDC%20Director%20Mandy%20Cohen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkffhealthnews.org%2Fmorning-breakout%2Fcdc-fda-officials-warn-kids-could-die-from-rfk-jr-s-anti-vaccine-stance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20a%20conference%20in%20Washington%20DC.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20see%20us%20go%20backward%20in%20order%20to%20remind%20ourselves%20that%20vaccines%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEncourage%20people%20to%20use%20more%20%26quot%3Bfunctional%20medicine%26quot%3B%20and%20make%20%26quot%3Balternative%26quot%3B%20healthcare%20mainstream%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20has%20said%20he'd%20push%20for%20more%20coverage%20of%20functional%20medicine%2C%20and%20devote%2050%25%20of%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%20budget%20to%20%26quot%3Bpreventive%2C%20alternative%20and%20holistic%20approaches%20to%20health.%26quot%3B%20Typically%2C%20visits%20to%20functional%20medicine%20doctors%2C%20and%20the%20kinds%20of%20tests%20and%20treatments%20they%20provide%20for%20health%20concerns%20like%20allergies%2C%20gut%20issues%2C%20or%20disease%20prevention%2C%20are%20not%20necessarily%20covered%20by%20traditional%20health%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20floated%20the%20idea%20of%20giving%20every%20American%20a%20Health%20Savings%20Account%20for%20medical%20spending%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20a%20debit%20card-like%20alternative%20to%20a%20traditional%20private%20healthcare%20plan.%20With%20a%20HSA%2C%20you%20put%20money%20you%20earn%20into%20a%20tax-free%20account%20to%20use%20for%20healthcare%20expenses%20like%20doctor's%20visits%20and%20prescriptions%2C%20instead%20of%20paying%20monthly%20premiums%20to%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrump-can-make-america-healthy-again-rfk-jr-reforms-chronic-disease-crisis-a9b4b8c0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopinion%20piece%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20published%20in%20September%2C%20Kennedy%20also%20said%20in%20wants%20to%20%26quot%3Breform%20the%20Prescription%20Drug%20User%20Fee%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20move%20he%20hopes%20would%20boost%20competition%20in%20the%20drug%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a747df1e-458d-41c6-be6f-aed4a6408629%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20big%20chunk%20of%20the%20other%20ideas%20Kennedy%20has%20for%20improving%20human%20health%20have%20to%20do%20with%20our%20nutrition%20and%20fitness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fruit%20loops%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67366d25fa0140cdd5639cbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKennedy%20wants%20to%20get%20some%20more%20artificial%20colors%20out%20of%20US%20cereals%3Cp%3E%3A%20Lindsey%20Nicholson%2FUCG%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20aimed%20at%20improving%20rates%20of%20chronic%20health%20issues%20like%20obesity%20and%20type%202%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20you%20have%20to%20be%20too%20smart%20to%20say%20we%20have%20a%20chronic%20disease%20crisis%20going%20on%20in%20this%20country%20that%20starts%20in%20childhood%20with%20terrible%20diets%2C%26quot%3B%20FDA%20Commissioner%20Robert%20Califf%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statnews.com%2F2024%2F11%2F12%2Ffda-commissioner-califf-trump-election-rfk-jr-public-health-food-nutrition%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20STAT.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20work%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Kennedy's%20biggest%20ideas%20on%20this%20front%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20rid%20of%20artificial%20food%20coloring%20and%20banning%20some%20additives%20and%20chemicals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Union%20has%20banned%20specific%20dyes%20like%20red%20%2340%2C%20which%20studies%20have%20linked%20to%20hyperactivity%20and%20neurobehavioral%20issues%20like%20ADHD%20in%20some%20kids.%20California%20is%20currently%20trying%20to%20copy%20the%20strategy%2C%20with%20limited%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20campaign%20trail%20with%20Trump%2C%20Kennedy%20has%20made%20Fruit%20Loops%20the%20poster%20child%20for%20this%20issue%2C%20pointing%20out%20how%20the%20US%20version%20contains%20more%20artificial%20colors%20and%20additives%20than%20versions%20sold%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnding%20FDA%20scrutiny%20of%20things%20like%20raw%20milk%20and%20supplements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20FDA%20is%20battling%20a%20%26quot%3Bwar%20on%20public%20health%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20suppressing%20the%20use%20of%20anything%20%26quot%3Bthat%20advances%20human%20health%20and%20can't%20be%20patented%20by%20Pharma.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRobertKennedyJr%2Fstatus%2F1849925311586238737%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOn%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20recently%20listed%20out%20the%20items%20he%20feels%20the%20agency%20is%20overregulating%3A%20%26quot%3Bpsychedelics%2C%20peptides%2C%20stem%20cells%2C%20raw%20milk%2C%20hyperbaric%20therapies%2C%20chelating%20compounds%2C%20ivermectin%2C%20hydroxychloroquine%2C%20vitamins%2C%20clean%20foods%2C%20sunshine%2C%20exercise%2C%20nutraceuticals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20does%20not%20tell%20consumers%20that%20they%20can't%20drink%20raw%20milk%2C%20take%20supplements%2C%20or%20enjoy%20sunshine%20and%20exercise.%20Rather%2C%20the%20agency%20often%20issues%20warnings%20about%20the%20health%20hazards%20of%20certain%20items.%20Raw%20milk%20increases%20your%20risk%20of%20developing%20E.%20coli%2C%20and%20in%20rare%20cases%20can%20be%20fatal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20is%20also%20responsible%20for%20ensuring%20drugs%20are%20safe%20and%20effective%20before%20they%20are%20put%20on%20the%20market.%20It%20doesn't%20approve%20dietary%20supplements%2C%20but%20the%20agency%20warns%20consumers%20when%20it%20finds%20contamination%20in%20our%20supplements%20and%20food%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanging%20the%20rules%20for%20food%20stamps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20doesn't%20want%20people%20to%20use%20SNAP%20benefits%20to%20buy%20ultra-processed%20foods.%20He%20has%20also%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20ban%20ultra-processed%20foods%20in%20school%20lunches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20rid%20of%20conflicts%20of%20interest%20and%20ties%20to%20food%20and%20drug%20companies%20at%20various%20federal%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20said%20he'd%20work%20to%20ensure%20members%20of%20the%20Dietary%20Guidelines%20Advisory%20Committee%20have%20no%20connections%20to%20food%20or%20drug%20companies.%20He%20also%20wants%20to%20reform%20farm%20subsides%2C%20cutting%20back%20on%20corn%20and%20soy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERequiring%20medical%20students%20at%20federally-funded%20institutions%20to%20take%20nutrition%20classes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDoctors%20only%20tend%20to%20receive%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fdiet-related-diseases-are-the-no-1-cause-of-death-in-the-us-yet-many-doctors-receive-little-to-no-nutrition-education-in-med-school-236217%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20nutrition%20education%20during%20medical%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EComing%20up%20with%20some%20new%20%26quot%3Bpresidential%20fitness%20standards%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20uncle%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20was%20right%20in%201960%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fstream%2Fthe-soft-american-kennedy%2FThe%2520Soft%2520American%2520-%2520Kennedy_djvu.txt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhen%20he%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20'The%20physical%20vigor%20of%20our%20citizens%20is%20one%20of%20America's%20most%20precious%20resources.'%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20recently%20wrote%20in%20an%20op-ed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22314334a6-b0ff-45de-83d9-23c9a86f7b1d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20also%20has%20a%20couple%20of%20ideas%20for%20Big%20Pharma%20reform%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy's%20said%20he%20wants%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENegotiate%20drug%20prices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20something%20a%20lot%20of%20countries%20do%2C%20but%20the%20US%20does%20not.%20Lots%20of%20politicians%20(like%20Bernie%20Sanders)%20have%20said%20this%20is%20something%20they%20want%20to%20do.%20In%20practice%2C%20it's%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanders.senate.gov%2Fpress-releases%2Fnews-sanders-statement-on-medicare-negotiating-drug-prices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epretty%20hard%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrack%20down%20on%20pharmaceutical%20ads%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20the%20US%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20places%20in%20the%20world%20where%20drugmakers%20can%20sell%20commercials%20that%20run%20in%20primetime%20TV%20and%20market%20drugs%20