h%20marketing%2C%20managing%20finances%2C%20and%20scaling%20their%20projects%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aryan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20experienced%20all%20of%20this%20firsthand%20when%20I%20was%20working%20on%20my%20own%20projects%20in%20Classes%209%20and%2010%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20tough%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20teenagers%2C%20this%20is%20a%20common%20dilemma.%20A%20bright%20idea%2C%20paired%20with%20enthusiasm%2C%20often%20collides%20with%20the%20harsh%20reality%20of%20turning%20that%20idea%20into%20a%20tangible%20product.%20But%20rather%20than%20giving%20up%2C%20Aryan%20decided%20to%20confront%20these%20obstacles%20head-on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20letting%20these%20challenges%20derail%20him%2C%20he%20used%20them%20as%20the%20motivation%20to%20create%20something%20new%3A%20%E2%80%98LaunchPad%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20free%20digital%20platform%20aimed%20at%20helping%20teenagers%20learn%20future-proof%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F275433%2Fcoding-for-children-online-classes-benefits-parenting-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskills%20and%20build%20real-world%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20spark%20behind%20LaunchPad%3A%20A%20platform%20for%20young%20entrepreneurs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAryan%E2%80%99s%20journey%20to%20LaunchPad%20began%20long%20before%20he%20set%20out%20to%20build%20his%20first%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20traces%20his%20love%20for%20creation%20back%20to%20childhood%2C%20recalling%20how%20he%20used%20to%20make%20intricate%20origami%20figures%20when%20he%20was%20nine.%20As%20he%20grew%20o