0beyond%20a%20school%20club%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295026%2Fhealthcare-startup-to-manage-pcos-for-indian-women-by-sisters-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20serves%20students%20across%2015%20schools%20in%20five%20countries.%20Today%2C%20the%20team%20has%20expanded%20to%20a%20dynamic%20group%20of%2015%20to%2020%20young%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunchPad%E2%80%99s%20mission%20is%20simple%3A%20to%20help%20students%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2012%20and%2017%20learn%20essential%20skills%20and%20gain%20hands-on%20experience%20in%20project%20development.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20learning%20how%20to%20code%20or%20design.%20LaunchPad%20focuses%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20future-proof%20skills%20that%20are%20vital%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20fast-changing%20world.%20These%20include%20design%20thinking%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337031%2Fbest-ai-innovations-by-indians-artificial-intelligence-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20foundations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20business%20fundamentals%2C%20storytelling%20and%20communication%2C%20and%20financial%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20the%20skills%20that%20will%20be%20relevant%20no%20matter%20what%20career%20path%20students%20choose%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aryan%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20the%20building%20blocks%20for%20anything%20they%20want%20to%20create%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20interactive%20modules%2C%20videos%2C%20expert%20interviews%2C%20presentations%2C%20and%20quizzes%2C%20LaunchPad%20helps%20students%20learn%20these%20skills%20in%20a%20fun%2C%20engaging%2C%20and%20effective%20way.%20Each%20module%20includes%20a%20guided%20assignment%2C%20designed%20to%20help%20students%20build%20their%20first%20project%20step-by-step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20in%20the%20design%20thinking%20module%2C%20students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20explore%20their%20passions%20through%20exercises%20like%20the%20Ikigai%20exercise%2C%20which%20helps%20them%20find%20the%20overlap%20between%20what%20they%20love%2C%20what%20they%E2%80%99re%20good%20at%2C%20and%20what%20problems%20they%20can%20solve%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aryan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasises%20that%20LaunchPad%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20accessible%20and%20engaging.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20content%20is%20designed%20for%20teenagers%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20too%20overwhelming%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20not%20too%20basic%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20students%20to%20feel%20like%20they%E2%80%99re%20learning%20real%2C%20practical%20skills%20that%20they%20can%20apply%20at%20their%20workplace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20early%20challenges%3A%20Launching%20the%20platform%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilding%20a%20platform%20like%20LaunchPad%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20without%20its%20challenges.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20hurdles%20Aryan%20faced%20was%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20get%20approval%20for%20the%20idea%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20how%20to%20spark%20interest%20among%20students%20about%20the%20website.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20pitched%20the%20idea%2C%20I%20went%20from%20class%20to%20class%2C%20speaking%20with%20students%20and%20noting%20down%20their%20names%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20faced%20many%20of%20the%20same%20obstacles%20that%20any%20young%20entrepreneur%20faces%20when%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20community.%20He%20realised%20that%20in%20order%20to%20grow%2C%20he%20needed%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20increase%20the%20click-through%20rate%20on%20the%20website%20and%20