20the%20visually%20impaired.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20often-overlooked%20realm%20of%20mental%20health%2C%20%E2%80%98Raahee%E2%80%99%20is%20making%20significant%20strides%20in%20providing%20accessible%20support%20and%20therapy.%20Through%20its%20empathetic%20and%20humanist%20approach%2C%20Raahee%E2%80%99s%20platform%20offers%20an%20application%20and%20website%20that%20connect%20users%20with%20therapists%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20With%20over%201%2C000%20users%20already%20benefiting%20from%20their%20services%2C%20Raahee%20is%20advancing%20the%20crucial%20social%20cause%20of%20making%20mental%20healthcare%20affordable%20and%20dismantling%20its%20associated%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20thingQbator%20programme%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98thingQbator%E2%80%99%20began%20in%202018%20as%20a%20maker%20space%20for%20Cisco%E2%80%99s%20engineers%20to%20don%20their%20innovation%20caps%20and%20transform%20their%20ideas%20into%20working%20prototypes.%20The%20success%20of%20this%20internal%20incubator%20prompted%20the%20company%20to%20scale%20it%20up%20in%20partnership%20with%20nasscom%20foundation%20and%20open%20it%20to%20universities%20across%20the%20country%20to%20promote%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20encompasses%20a%20four-stage%20programme%2C%20nurturing%20the%20transformation%20of%20ideas%20into%20thriving%20ventures.%20From%20the%20ideation%20stage%20to%20incubation%2C%20the%20top%2010%20teams%20are%20granted%20a%20seed%20fund%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20marking%20the%20transition%20of%20their%20social%20ventures%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seventh%20edition%20of%20thingQbator%20is%20currently%20underway%2C%20mentoring%20and%20nurturing%20undergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20students%20with%20a%20vision%20aligned%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%E2%80%99%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3