rt%2C%20the%20artist%2C%20and%20yourself%2C%20but%20the%20children%20are%20simply%20not%20learning%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharon%2C%20a%20Tamilian%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20she%20has%20been%20working%20in%20the%20social%20development%20sector%20for%20about%2014%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20youth%20from%20these%20artist%20communities%20still%20want%20to%20learn%20and%20pursue%20music%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20space%20for%20them%20to%20play%20or%20learn.%20You%E2%80%99ll%20find%20hundreds%20of%20people%20who%20can%20play%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekhartal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(hand%20cymbal)%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20only%20a%20handful%20who%20can%20play%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekamaicha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20bowed%20instrument%20with%20a%20large%2C%20wooden%2C%20bowl-shaped%20resonator%20covered%20with%20skin).%20Same%20is%20the%20case%20with%20%3Cem%3Esarangi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20stringed%20instrument%20played%20with%20a%20bow)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ealghoza%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emorchang%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhati%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Bhati%E2%80%99s%20Rajasthani%20band%20went%20viral%20on%20Netflix%2C%20reviving%20folk%20music%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhati%20soon%20initiated%20projects%20to%20bring%20young%20Rajasthani%20voices%20to%20the%20cultural%20forefront.%20His%20first%20major%20success%20was%20the%20band%20%3Cem%3ERaitila%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20comprising%20seven%20to%20eight%20young%20men%20from%20folk%20music%20backgrounds.%20They%20trained%20and%20rehearsed%20for%20about%20six%20months%2C%20resulting%20in%20their%20debut%20song%20%3Cem%3EMehman%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20composed%20and%20arranged%20by%20Bhati%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20track%20gained%20immense%20popularity%2C%20even%20being%20featured%20in%20the%20second%20season%20of%20the%20popular%20Netflix%20show%20%3Cem%3EMismat