8%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20wanted%20was%20to%20make%20people%20realise%20that%20these%20artists%20are%20worth%20the%20money%20and%20time%20just%20as%20much%20as%20others%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhati%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20how%20folk%20artists%20have%20not%20been%20given%20their%20due%20diligence%20in%20a%20long%20time%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20certain%20perception%20people%20have%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20folk%20artists.%20If%20you%20go%20to%20an%20event%20organiser%20and%20say%20you%20have%20some%20folk%20artists%20who%E2%80%99d%20love%20to%20perform%2C%20the%20artist%20fee%20immediately%20cuts%20in%20half%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20the%20funds%20are%20coming%20from%20a%20private%20organisation%20or%20the%20Government.%20What%20we%20wanted%20was%20to%20make%20people%20realise%20that%20these%20artists%20are%20worth%20the%20money%20and%20time%20just%20as%20much%20as%20others%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20these%20initial%20projects%20gained%20enough%20traction%2C%20Bhati%20and%20his%20team%20kept%20meeting%20new%20people%20and%20patrons%20who%20wanted%20to%20help.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20got%20our%20footing%20right%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20these%20artists%E2%80%99%20development%20also.%20So%2C%20we%20started%20%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEducating%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20Rajasthani%20folk%20artists%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202023%2C%20%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20fully%20funded%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365250%2Fvinyasa-earth-sankalp-sharma-sustainable-homestay-jaipur-artist-residencies-mud-bamboo-cob-lime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartist%20residency%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20young%20children%20from%20across%20Rajasthan%20can%20gather%20to%20learn%20folk%20music%20from%20maestros%20and%20gurus.%20This%20initiative%20is%20groundbreaking%20because%2C%20unlike%20Indian%20classical%20music%2C%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20educational%20structure%20for%20folk%20music.%20Traditionally%2C%20it%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20orally%20through%20generations%2C%20with%20no%20written%20records%20to%20preserve%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residency%20spans%20seven%20days%20and%20includes%20nine%20classes%20covering%20various%20disciplines%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20vocals%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekamaicha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emurli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flute)%2C%20%3Cem%3Etandura%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tamboura)%2C%20and%20more.%20Currently%2C%20the%20programme%20works%20with%20three%20folk%20music%20communities%3A%20%3Cem%3ELanga%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EMeghwal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EManganiyars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20allowing%20students%20to%20learn%20directly%20from%20master%20artists%20of%20these%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20dignitaries%20like%20Lakha%20Khan%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20and%20the%20maestro%20of%20Sarangi%2C%20give%20masterclasses%20here.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20go%20to%20foreign%20countries%20or%20even%20other%20states%20to%20play%2C%20the%20reception%20is%20good%20because%20the%20type%20of%20people%20who%20come%20to%20watch%20us%20actually%20value%20folk%20singing.%20So%2C%20people%20do%20like%20it.%20But%20it%20is%20important%20to%20actually%20teach%20kids%20and%20make%20them%20understand%20what%20it%20means%20because%20only%20then%20will%20this%20art%20be%20able%20to%20survive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%203269px)%20100vw%2C%203269px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201.jpg%5C%22%