20ingredients%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEighty-year-old%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268194%2Fgujju-ben-na-nasta-mumbai-best-breakfast-inspiring-woman-entrepreneur-grandmother-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUrmila%20Asher%20helms%20%E2%80%98Gujju%20Ben%20Na%20Nasta%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20brand%20that%20prides%20itself%20on%20homemade%20Gujarati%20snacks.%20And%20today%20she%20is%20here%20to%20ensure%20your%20%3Cem%3Eundhiyu%20%3C%2Fem%3Eturns%20out%20perfect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FDMDYZRskPB8%3Fsi%3DYYqi0RKJHuWaz5rb%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%E2%80%98poster%20dish%E2%80%99%20of%20Gujarati%20cuisine%2C%20whose%20appearance%20on%20the%20dinner%20%3Cem%3Ethali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(plate)%20is%20indicative%20of%20winter%20onset%2C%20goes%20beyond%20being%20a%20delicious%20addition.%20Prepared%20with%20seasonal%20vegetables%2C%20such%20as%20brinjals%2C%20green%20beans%2C%20and%20sweet%20potatoes%2C%20the%20dish%20packs%20a%20punch%20in%20every%20mouthful.%20While%20every%20region%20has%20its%20unique%20spin%20on%20the%20speciality%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%3Cem%3Eundhiyu%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Ahmedabad%20tends%20to%20be%20spicy%20and%20slightly%20heavier%20on%20oil%2C%20and%20the%20one%20in%20Surat%20is%20garlicky%20%E2%80%94%20every%20version%20is%20undeniably%20a%20feast%20for%20the%20senses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20%3Cem%3EDhuaan%20Maas%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMutton%20is%20a%20winter%20obvious.%20And%20this%20time-tested%20recipe%20borrows%20from%20diasporic%20culinary%20traditions.%20It%20has%20come%20down%20through%20generations%20of%20chef%20Amrita%20Raichand%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20historically%20being%20cooked%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20chulha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(earthen%20stove).%20%E2%80%9CI%20took%20it%20%5Bthe%20dish%5D%20back%20to%20the%20roots%20by%20re-creating%20a%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20chulha%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20gave%20it%20a%20final%20touch%20with%20%E2%80%98coal%20smoke%E2%80%99%20bringing%20in%20the%20authentic%20flavours.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FrvEAygGNhzI%3Fsi%3DUAk57HbUIs_-az1J%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349748%2Flaal-maas-history-recipe-best-places-to-eat-in-rajasthan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajasthani%20delicacies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Edhuaan%20maas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20reflective%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20rich%20cultural%20history%20woven%20with%20royal%20lore.%20It%20still%20imbues%20the%20extensive%20preparatory%20process%20that%20once%20went%20into%20curating%20the%20dish%20for%20the%20royals%20who%20feasted%20on%20it%20following%20hunting%20expeditions.%20The%20name%20too%20borrows%20from%20the%20meat%20being%20slow-cooked%20over%20charcoal%2C%20allowing%20the%20spices%20and%20flavours%20to%20really%20seep%20in.%20The%20result%20is%20a%20mouthful%20of%20succulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20%3Cem%3EKand%20Tikkis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwap%20your%20guilty%20pleasure%20snacks%20with%20some%20%3Cem%3Ekand%20tikkis%3C%2Fem%3E%20this%20winter!%20Best%20selling%20cookery%20author%20Tarla%20Dalal%E2%80%99s%20inventive%20take%20on%20%3Cem%3Etikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(fried%20patties)%20combines%20the%20